hopobject.body: How do you know each other? social clinical and surgical hand washing Restructuring talks involving the various vertical and horizontal classes of creditor (or representative e.g. the special servicer) have already been going on for more than a year. Given the significant capital expenditure requirements across the portfolio, and in light of the likely depressive effect of on-going government austerity measures on occupancy levels, further delays would likely have a negative effect on values. According to the reported portfolio value, the loan-to-value ratio is about 100%, which Fitch considers an under-estimate of risk.
